title: 116: Our Scariest Horror Movie Experiences | Ear Biscuits Ep. 116
description:
Rhett & Link sit down to discuss all things horror movies -- from Rhett's annual horror movie birthday tradition to Link's recollections about the first time he saw The Texas Chainsaw Massacre on this week's Ear Biscuits.
